* Description

  This repository is for CM9 on HTC marvel.
  It is still a work in progress.


* How To Build CM9 for HTC Marvel

  Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/android/system
  $ cd ~/android/system

  Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/CyanogenMod/android.git -b ics

  Create .repo/local_manifest.xml with the following content:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <manifest>
      <project name="CyanogenMod/android_device_htc_common" path="device/htc/common" revision="refs/heads/gingerbread" />
      <project name="gladiac/android_device_htc_marvel" path="device/htc/marvel" />
      <project name="gladiac/proprietary_vendor_htc" path="vendor/htc" />
  </manifest>

  $ repo sync

  Setup vendor

  $ cd vendor/cm
  $ ./get-prebuilts

  Setup environment

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch cm_marvel-eng


  Build CM9

  $ make -j4 bacon


* Thanks

  Cyanogen
  alquez

